Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不能使用忍術和幻術
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能成為出色的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.30,0:01:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是要證明這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我意志的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我會更努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.80,0:02:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濃眉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手婆婆給你看過病了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉現在百廢待興
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們如果不加油可說不過去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濃眉快點把傷治好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.59,0:02:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後和我們一起執行任務吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸他…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:02:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把自己關起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己關起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之意志的繼承者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸少爺 我們要進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們以為我是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有本事就試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是第三代的孫子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們如果冒犯我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是冒犯火影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是綱手大人必須盡快開始工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是摻了胡椒粉的煙霧彈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再敢靠近的話 有你們受的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫少爺 就算是孫少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是什麼事都可以做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼一大早就大吵大鬧的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵得我頭都疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個小鬼在裡面幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把他拖出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 在裡面的是第三代的孫子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他是孫子還是曾孫子 都沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是身為初代孫女的我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教訓他一下對他也有好處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把他弄出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請 請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不太清楚狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但請不要對木葉丸動粗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:04:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好啊 綱手婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來說服他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在今天之內搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人 請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小櫻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助昨天就出院了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我是來看小李的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他來理療恢復室了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪啊 他很少遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手術成功率最高也就50%
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗的話就是死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點出來 我帶你去吃拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 今天由我買單哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 是叉燒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 再加一個雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是吱一聲 給個回應啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說我是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快開門 否則我硬闖了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有本事就放馬過來試試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小李
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助已經出院回家療養了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他馬上就能執行任務了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.10,0:07:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是綱手大人 真是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人一定會治癒小李的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 如果有我可以幫忙的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管開口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼沒有一家酒店開著門呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想也不可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您以為現在幾點了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不能喝酒 又不能賭一把
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉還真是無聊透頂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像第三代一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想找個地方坐下來喝杯熱的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就帶您去一個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以坐下好好喝一杯熱飲的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為交換 您可要開工了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 盡情喝吧 這可是熱的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然變得很嚴格了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我變嚴格了 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是綱手大人太不自覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不進那個房間就無法工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就想「不做也罷」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就全部交給鳴人去解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最新的忍者名單
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面的成員和分組也作了不少變動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您大概地看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:09:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概地全部看一遍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有糰子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭甜食了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧了 快出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少 你要告訴我究竟出什麼事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不明事理的話 我就要拽你出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人奧義.色誘之術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就出來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸 快嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 你至少也說點什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是太丟人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再胡鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許再胡鬧了 木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這究竟是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 鳴人哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是爺爺的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D級任務8次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C級3次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是紅帶的班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三代的想法很好猜嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他們父親時的那組一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:11:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 這一組各有所長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可謂實力最均衡的一組吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰酸了 出去透透氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:13:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功 成功…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你玩真的 那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是爺爺的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了爺爺之外誰也不許用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為孫子 我要保護這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是說這個的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可是木葉的非常時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣 這與我毫無關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可激怒我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的新絕招破壞一兩道門還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可是緊要關頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子的實力僅存一半左右了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但任務還得接
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些好像都是我告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不接任務
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等於告訴別人我們不行了 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這句是伊魯卡老師說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜歡綱手婆婆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過不了多久就沒有人叫我孫少爺了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會叫我木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你木葉丸有什麼不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不喜歡別人叫你孫少爺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺在人們的記憶中逐漸消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們忘了爺爺是多麼出色的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像處理他的煙箱一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的火影會不斷地深入人心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒這回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉就是木葉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 大家是不會忘記爺爺的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 應該是絕對忘不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會的 一定會的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我的話都不信了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:16:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來 木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去找綱手婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她保證 不要改變木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 讓大家保證不忘掉爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.85,0:17:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然讓綱手大人脫離了我的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了嗎 豚豚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,細胞活性化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可找到你了 綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人在學習
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩不煩啊 無法集中精力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我第一次在賭錢以外聽到這話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜音大姐的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得那名叫兜的醫療忍者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有製造新細胞的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想用這招來增補患者的細胞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了小李嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只能提升1%的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有嘗試的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個很依賴各人的資質
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是綱手大人也很難掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行也得行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是第五代火影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒辦法啊 木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是第三代火影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想幹就別幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉是一個大家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護家庭成員就是火影的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天例外哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.15,0:19:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去找綱手婆婆了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行也得行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是第五代火影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒辦法啊 木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是第三代火影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是孫少爺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 我是木葉的木葉丸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.45,0:20:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸 等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時凱老師告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.91,0:22:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要和強力的死對頭競爭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會成為了不起的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.85,0:22:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首要條件就是努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.21,0:22:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心情輕鬆多了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.21,0:22:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來不知道該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經知道該怎麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要努力就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.39,0:22:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.50,0:22:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.26,0:23:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱血師徒的羈絆 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢貫徹忍道的時候到了
